Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,兩次鼓動 兜的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經…完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這風中的殘燭一般 顫抖不止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她毫無痛苦地死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…為了佐助 什麼都能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求你了 留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…佐助在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這副肉體就是佐助的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒必要再隱瞞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜 你就告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是來晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人沒能等到佐助的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經轉生到別的容器裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說佐助沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就在這裏的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人為了等待下一次轉生的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經給佐助下了咒印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非所有的人都能承受這個咒印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助沒能承受住咒印 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 你撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定是在撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒謊對我而言 又有什麼好處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反正…也快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼想見他 就成全你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了以後 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就能在那個世界重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 這種傢伙說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你早就死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把佐助給帶回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 你在這裏躲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪里啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦無用光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我痛快地揍你一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些煩人的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.霧炎舞之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你和大蛇丸都在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 佐助也在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…動不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看看自己的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是查克拉線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉…線…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你剛才攻擊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把線纏到了你的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這線通向哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己好好看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條查克拉線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我心臟的經脈相通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏在你身上的線 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過你的經脈 內臟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的心臟相連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的心臟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就會合二為一了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用查克拉凝結的線 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對無法扯斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的心臟已經完全同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我的心臟發出的查克拉線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過經脈支配了你的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 明明是我的心臟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心跳加速的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心跳也會變快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心臟不再跳動時…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止心臟跳動的話 你也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這沒什麼不大了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的這副身體早已獻給大蛇丸大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要幹嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我捏碎了這顆心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會…死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我捏碎了這顆心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會…死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 和我一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種心臟被握在手中的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就會變得輕鬆起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你殺了我 鳴人也會死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要砍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用查克拉凝結的線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能切斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是綱手大人的怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法扯斷它的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人就在我面前痛苦地掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻什麼忙也幫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…絕對不會輸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我…完成自己的承諾之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞強到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一塊兒同歸於盡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一塊兒到佐助等候著我們的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這張符貼到苦無上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我的胸口跳得一塌糊塗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我白擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧莎莎美救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那個陷阱裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大水沖了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個陷阱的蓋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當水淹到天花板的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼命想打開陷阱的蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無奈紋絲不動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自來也大人要我到半崎那兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我怎麼也放心不下嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑過來一看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我怎麼推
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能打開蓋子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼用苦無無法切斷的線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼上了莎莎美的符後就切斷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們風馬忍法奧義中的奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風馬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙又是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜉蝣大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是風馬的上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人復活了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 被大蛇丸給騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐呢 莎莎美的表哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們風馬一族…拉上了忍者的正面舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把真相告訴莎莎美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美和嵐 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人以前的關係可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 相見不如懷念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜉蝣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏等我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那裏有什麼在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了見嵐哥哥才來到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就一起過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許裏邊會有什麼機關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嵐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟…是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用風馬上忍的忍術把肉體融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了最強的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你見識一下我最強的忍術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 嵐哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕饒不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我還是什麼都沒做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是拖你的後腿 毫無改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是鳴人 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們教會了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想改變一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:22:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次輪到我來努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻的決心
